I haven't learned how to do any of this type of stuff yet, but I believe you want to look into 'templates', as you can do 'normal' templates, 'verb' templates, and 'dynamic verb' templates.

<!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://docs.textadventures.co.uk/quest/guides/using_templates.html">http://docs.textadventures.co.uk/quest/ ... lates.html</a><!-- m -->

