Many of Pixie's Libraries, such as (I'm pretty sure anyways):

Pixie's RPG-style Combat Library: <!-- l --><a class="postlink-local" href="http://forum.textadventures.co.uk/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=4886#p32783">viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=4886#p32783</a><!-- l -->

